tle\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shane Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anthea Moodie\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just over two months ago, the 50-year-old team eventer was thrown from his horse in an accident he has no memory of, which resulted in 18 bone breaks, multiple surgeries and having to learn to walk again.\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 50-year-old team eventer\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"his horse\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"an accident\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"no memory\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"18 bone breaks\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple surgeries\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But right from the moment he fell, he had just one goal in mind.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"just one goal\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My wife played a little clip of when I was on the ground and unconscious, not knowing what I was doing, and my first question was; 'how long have I got to go to the [Olympic] Games?'\\\"\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My wife\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"a little clip\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 744}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"my first question\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"the [Olympic] Games\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rose said.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 900, \"end\": 904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.999966819036928, \"rank\": 2.5359777756731738e-05, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was always really confident that I could get back, I am still really confident that I will be ready to go.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of things have had to have gone right and, touch wood, so far they have been going really well.\\\"\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"right and, touch wood\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shane Rose says he did not feel nervous to get back on his horse Virgil after his fall.\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\", \"score\": 0.9669469470264936, \"rank\": 0.02898281570316557, \"text\": \"Virgil\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shane Rose\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"his horse\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"his fall\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Facebook: Shane Rose Eventing) Since then, that goal has only become more achievable.\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shane Rose Eventing\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"that goal\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rose recently returned to his Werombi home, south-west of Sydney, and rode a horse for the first time since his accident.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1334, \"end\": 1341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Werombi,_New_South_Wales\", \"score\": 0.669467902590356, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Werombi\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Werombi,_New_South_Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Werombi,_New_South_Wales\"}, {\"begin\": 1362, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 6.792795303775031e-12, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rose\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"a horse\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"his accident\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not tell anyone how sore it was [getting on a horse for the first time] \\u2026 but fortunately within a few minutes, [the pain] really eased off and it felt quite good,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"a horse\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"a few minutes\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"the pain\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not feel nervous at all about getting back on.\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every time I have got on it's felt better, from the start right through, and just keeps improving.\\\"\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rose spent about a month at the Australian Institute of Sport (AIS), where he lived onsite and had three sessions a day to fast-track his rehabilitation.\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1829, \"end\": 1832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Institute_of_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6763235569795374e-15, \"text\": \"AIS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Institute_of_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Institute_of_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rose\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"the Australian Institute\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"three sessions\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"his rehabilitation\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Part of Rose's rehabilitation included exercises on a stationary bike with a hobby horse attached to the front.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1929, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.999966819036928, \"rank\": 2.5359777756731738e-05, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Part\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"exercises\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"a stationary bike\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"a hobby horse\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Instagram: Shane Rose Eventing) He said the progression he felt in a short time was huge.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Instagram\", \"from\": 2032, 